{"item_id":"245fb95024:0","text":"此节点会创建受控随机变化。变化源可以基于 attribute 或 primvar。primvar 应具有 constant detail（每个 object 一个单一值）。只有非零 id/primvar/attribute 值才会创建变化。如果无法读取源，则不会产生变化。能够查找任意 float 或 int attribute，是调试场景的好方法。例如，如果你想知道哪些 object 是 single-sided（单面），可以在 varName 中输入 'Ri:Sides'。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:1","text":"Input Parameters"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:2","text":"Input Color"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:3","text":"你想要施加变化的颜色。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:4","text":"Vary Source"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:5","text":"变化源，可为以下之一："}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:6","text":"0: Identifier Id"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:7","text":"1: Identifier Name"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:8","text":"2: Primvar"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:9","text":"3: Attribute"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:10","text":"Variable Name"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:11","text":"如果 varySource 为 1 或 2，则这里是 primvar 或 user attribute 的名称。如果使用 primvar，它应为 constant；不支持 per-vertex/face primvars。对于 user attributes，请输入 \""}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:12","text":"Hue"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:13","text":"限制随机 hue（色相）偏移。范围从 0（无变化）到 1（完整变化）。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:14","text":"Saturation"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:15","text":"限制随机 saturation scale（饱和度缩放）。范围从 0（无变化）到 1（完整变化）。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:16","text":"Luminance"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:17","text":"限制随机 luminance scale（亮度缩放）。范围从 0（无变化）到 1（完整变化）。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:18","text":"Gamma"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:19","text":"限制随机 gamma 变化。范围从 0（无变化）到 1（完整变化）。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:20","text":"Advanced"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:21","text":"Probability"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:22","text":"0 到 1 的范围指定应用变化的可能性。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:23","text":"Hue Mode"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:24","text":"颜色 hue 将如何变化："}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:25","text":"0: Centered -- 变化会以当前值为中心。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:26","text":"1: Additive -- 变化会添加到当前值。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:27","text":"2: Subtractive -- 变化会从当前值中减去。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:40","text":"0: Centered -- 变化会以当前值为中心。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:41","text":"1: Additive -- 变化会添加到当前值。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:42","text":"2: Subtractive -- 变化会从当前值中减去。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:28","text":"Saturation Mode"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:29","text":"颜色 saturation 将如何变化："}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:30","text":"0: Centered -- 变化会以当前值为中心。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:31","text":"1: Additive -- 变化会添加到当前值。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:32","text":"2: Subtractive -- 变化会从当前值中减去。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:33","text":"Luminance Mode"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:34","text":"颜色 luminance 将如何变化："}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:35","text":"0: Centered -- 变化会以当前值为中心。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:36","text":"1: Additive -- 变化会添加到当前值。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:37","text":"2: Subtractive -- 变化会从当前值中减去。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:38","text":"Gamma Mode"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:39","text":"颜色 gamma 将如何变化："}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:43","text":"Seed"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:44","text":"允许在不改变已设置 primvar 的情况下改变变化结果"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:45","text":"Scale Normalized Primvar"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:46","text":"对于 primvar scale 超出 normalized range 的项目，会取已设置的 primvars，并将它们缩放到 pattern 使用的预期 0-1 范围"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:47","text":"Verbosity"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:48","text":"输出各种信息以帮助你调试场景。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:49","text":"0: Silent -- 仅输出错误消息。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:50","text":"1: Warnings -- 报告错误和缺失的 attributes。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:51","text":"2: Infos -- 与上面相同，并额外输出 attributes 的值。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:52","text":"Output Parameters"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:65","text":"resultRGB"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:54","text":"clamp 后的颜色结果。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:55","text":"resultR"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:56","text":"R 通道来自"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:58","text":"输出。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:66","text":"输出。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:59","text":"resultG"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:60","text":"G 通道来自"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:62","text":"输出。"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:63","text":"resultB"}
{"item_id":"245fb95024:64","text":"B 通道来自"}
{"id": "d76cd2ea3537dbac1a9b90ba977fe5ad654d6f7f3c36b060963224d8b5611f99", "item_id": "245fb95024:53", "text": "resultRGB"}
